Goal 		: Add  signal handling

Given 		: Makefile, header file , test harness shell, parser,
		  builtin, run_command is_background redirect_in
		  redirect_out pipe_present pipe_command

Required	: parent ignores signals ; child reverts to default
		  Modify shell.c and run_command.c

Optional	: Add SIGCHLD signal handler to reap background processes
		  (Start with the example in chapter 6 text.)

Course Ref	: sigset(3C), sigaction(2), waitpid(2)
